WEBVTT

00:00.030 --> 00:02.599
I want to do
something original. Unique!

00:02.600 --> 00:04.735
You could paint
your perfect painting, Pablo.

00:04.736 --> 00:07.771
These paintings, they
were the best work I've ever done.

00:07.772 --> 00:10.407
I've had my work destroyed before.

00:10.408 --> 00:13.943
And the Nazis have labeled
every bit of it as degenerate.

00:13.945 --> 00:16.146
It is extraordinary, Pablo.

00:16.146 --> 00:17.848
It's a gift, Uncle.

00:17.849 --> 00:19.750
To thank you for everything
you've done for me.

00:19.751 --> 00:21.280
I made to vow to God that if he let

00:21.281 --> 00:23.144
Conchita live I would
give up painting.

00:24.189 --> 00:26.123
God knew I could
never keep my promise.

00:26.124 --> 00:29.326
So, he punished me. He took her.

00:30.295 --> 00:31.929
The roses are exquisite, Hervé.

00:31.930 --> 00:33.463
Thank you, Monsieur.

00:33.464 --> 00:35.999
There are thorns. Be careful.

00:36.000 --> 00:37.201
Never.

00:37.202 --> 00:38.802
Who is this woman, Pablo?

00:38.803 --> 00:40.637
I am Dora Maar. And
you must be Marie-Thérèse.

00:42.841 --> 00:44.942
I will never be bored by you.

00:45.977 --> 00:48.178
My name is Carles Casagemas.

00:48.179 --> 00:50.747
What is yours?

00:50.915 --> 00:52.316
Picasso.

00:52.317 --> 00:53.884
Picasso and I, we are the future.

00:53.885 --> 00:55.185
I don't understand you, Francoise.

00:55.186 --> 00:56.820
I want to be a painter.

00:56.821 --> 00:58.121
You will become a lawyer.

00:58.122 --> 00:59.489
Do I make myself clear?

00:59.490 --> 01:01.550
Franco and his
fanatics are winning the war.

01:02.527 --> 01:05.295
Franco has Hitler and the
Nazis on his side, Pablo.

01:05.830 --> 01:07.865
We need you on ours.

01:07.866 --> 01:08.978
I know you didn't want to make

01:08.979 --> 01:10.868
a painting for the Spanish Pavilion,

01:10.869 --> 01:12.569
but now you must.

01:12.570 --> 01:15.405
I am going to need a very big canvas.

01:16.507 --> 01:18.275
I'm getting my family to safety.

01:18.276 --> 01:20.644
Guernica made the Nazis very angry.

01:21.012 --> 01:23.947
You have children. Women you love.

01:23.948 --> 01:26.350
Some things are more
important than art.

01:26.351 --> 01:27.818
Not to me.

